                        <rs type="title">Sophistry, or Curious Proofs and Arguments: from <lb/>the
                            Greek Sophists</rs> (<abbr>v.</abbr>
                        <rs type="name" key="P29">Funck-Brentano</rs>, <rs type="title">Les<lb/>
